## 📌 What Is This?

Most people come to cybersecurity from a purely technical background.

I didn’t.

I came from **project management** — timelines, stakeholders, risk registers, delivery plans. And what I quickly realized is that security *needs* that structure. Badly.

This repo is a collection of **templates, frameworks, and documents** that bridge the gap between security and project management. Free to use, adapt, and build on.

